Dann schaue in die **MAMP Log-Dateien**:
- `/Applications/MAMP/logs/php_error.log` (macOS)
- `C:\MAMP\logs\php_error.log` (Windows)

## Alternative: Frontend mit FormData (falls JSON nicht funktioniert)

Falls die Body Parsing Middleware nicht hilft, ändere das Frontend auf `FormData`:

**In `param-management.html`, ersetze die Fetch-Anfrage:**

```javascript
reader.onload = async (e) => {
    const xmlContent = e.target.result;
    const projectName = file.name.replace('.xml', '') + '.gsm';

    statusMessage.textContent = 'Status: Parameter werden importiert...';

    const apiUrl = 'http://localhost:8888/gdl-ui-studio/backend/public/api/parameters/import';

    try {
        // ÄNDERUNG: Verwende FormData statt JSON
        const formData = new FormData();
        formData.append('xml_content', xmlContent);
        formData.append('project_name', projectName);

        const response = await fetch(apiUrl, {
            method: 'POST',
            body: formData,  // Kein Content-Type Header nötig bei FormData!
        });

        const result = await response.json();

        if (response.ok) {
            statusMessage.textContent = `Status: ${result.message}`;
            currentProjectId = result.projectId;
            currentProjectNameSpan.textContent = `Projekt: ${projectName}`;
            console.log('Import successful:', result);
            displayParameters(currentProjectId);
        } else {
            statusMessage.textContent = `Fehler: ${result.error || 'Unbekannter Fehler'}`;
            console.error('Import failed:', result);
        }
    } catch (error) {
        statusMessage.textContent = `Netzwerkfehler: ${error.message}`;
        console.error('Network or other error:', error);
    }
};
```

## Was hat sich geändert?

1. **`addBodyParsingMiddleware()`** - Slim 4 parst JSON standardmäßig nicht automatisch
2. **Debug-Logging** - um zu sehen, was ankommt
3. **FormData Alternative** - falls JSON-Parsing Probleme macht

**Teste zuerst mit der Body Parsing Middleware**, das ist die sauberste Lösung!

Nach dem Test kannst du die Debug-Zeilen wieder entfernen.

Ah! **Syntax-Fehler in Zeile 177** der `ParameterController.php`! 

Du hast wahrscheinlich beim Einfügen der Debug-Zeilen versehentlich eine geschweifte Klammer `}` gelöscht oder an der falschen Stelle eingefügt.

## Schnelle Lösung: Hier ist die komplette, fehlerfreie ParameterController.php

```php
<?php
namespace App\Controllers;

use Psr\Http\Message\ResponseInterface as Response;
use Psr\Http\Message\ServerRequestInterface as Request;
use \PDO;

class ParameterController
{
    protected PDO $db;

    public function __construct(PDO $db)
    {
        $this->db = $db;
    }

    // Helper function to return JSON responses
    private function jsonResponse(Response $response, array $data, int $status = 200): Response
    {
        $response->getBody()->write(json_encode($data));
        return $response
            ->withHeader('Content-Type', 'application/json')
            ->withStatus($status);
    }

    public function importXml(Request $request, Response $response): Response
    {
        // ========== DEBUG START ==========
        error_log("=== REQUEST DEBUG ===");
        error_log("Content-Type: " . $request->getHeaderLine('Content-Type'));
        $bodyContents = $request->getBody()->getContents();
        error_log("Raw Body Length: " . strlen($bodyContents));
        error_log("Raw Body Preview: " . substr($bodyContents, 0, 200)); // Erste 200 Zeichen
        $request->getBody()->rewind(); // Wichtig! Body zurückspulen
        // ========== DEBUG END ==========

        $data = $request->getParsedBody();
        error_log("Parsed Body Type: " . gettype($data));
        error_log("Parsed Body: " . print_r($data, true));

        $xmlContent = $data['xml_content'] ?? null;
        $projectName = $data['project_name'] ?? 'Default Project';

        if (empty($xmlContent)) {
            error_log("ERROR: No XML content provided. Data received: " . print_r($data, true));
            return $this->jsonResponse($response, [
                'error' => 'No XML content provided.',
                'debug' => [
                    'data_type' => gettype($data),
                    'data_keys' => is_array($data) ? array_keys($data) : 'not an array'
                ]
            ], 400);
        }

        try {
            $this->db->beginTransaction();

            // Create or get project
            $stmt = $this->db->prepare("INSERT INTO projects (name) VALUES (?) ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE updated_at=CURRENT_TIMESTAMP");
            $stmt->execute([$projectName]);
            $projectId = $this->db->lastInsertId();

            if ($projectId == 0) {
                $stmt = $this->db->prepare("SELECT id FROM projects WHERE name = ?");
                $stmt->execute([$projectName]);
                $projectId = $stmt->fetchColumn();
            }

            if (!$projectId) {
                throw new \Exception("Could not determine project ID.");
            }

            // Delete existing parameters
            $deleteTranslationsStmt = $this->db->prepare("DELETE FROM parameter_translations WHERE param_id IN (SELECT id FROM parameters WHERE project_id = ?)");
            $deleteTranslationsStmt->execute([$projectId]);
            $deleteParametersStmt = $this->db->prepare("DELETE FROM parameters WHERE project_id = ?");
            $deleteParametersStmt->execute([$projectId]);

            // Parse XML
            libxml_use_internal_errors(true);
            $xml = simplexml_load_string($xmlContent);
            if ($xml === false) {
                $xmlErrors = libxml_get_errors();
                $errorMessages = array_map(fn($error) => trim($error->message), $xmlErrors);
                libxml_clear_errors();
                throw new \Exception('Invalid XML format: ' . implode(', ', $errorMessages));
            }

            if (!isset($xml->Parameters)) {
                throw new \Exception("XML is missing the <Parameters> root element.");
            }

            $sortOrder = 0;
            foreach ($xml->Parameters->children() as $gdlParameter) {
                $sortOrder++;
                $gdlName = (string)$gdlParameter['Name'];
                $gdlType = $gdlParameter->getName();

                $description = '';
                if (isset($gdlParameter->Description)) {
                    $description = (string)$gdlParameter->Description;
                }

                $defaultValue = null;
                if (isset($gdlParameter->Value)) {
                    if ($gdlType === 'Dictionary') {
                        $defaultValue = json_encode(simplexml_to_array($gdlParameter->Value));
                    } else {
                        $defaultValue = (string)$gdlParameter->Value;
                    }
                } elseif (isset($gdlParameter->ArrayValues)) {
                    $arrayValues = [];
                    foreach($gdlParameter->ArrayValues->children() as $aVal) {
                        $arrayValues[] = (string)$aVal;
                    }
                    $defaultValue = json_encode($arrayValues);
                }

                // Extract flags
                $isFixName = isset($gdlParameter->Fix);
                $flagBold = false;
                $flagChild = false;
                $flagHidden = false;
                $flagUnique = false;

                if (isset($gdlParameter->Flags)) {
                    foreach ($gdlParameter->Flags->children() as $flag) {
                        switch ($flag->getName()) {
                            case 'ParFlg_BoldName': $flagBold = true; break;
                            case 'ParFlg_Child': $flagChild = true; break;
                            case 'ParFlg_Hidden': $flagHidden = true; break;
                            case 'ParFlg_Unique': $flagUnique = true; break;
                        }
                    }
                }

                $arrayType = 'None';
                $firstDim = 0;
                $secondDim = 0;
                if (isset($gdlParameter->ArrayValues)) {
                    $arrayType = ((int)$gdlParameter->ArrayValues['SecondDimension'] > 0) ? '2D' : '1D';
                    $firstDim = (int)$gdlParameter->ArrayValues['FirstDimension'];
                    $secondDim = (int)$gdlParameter->ArrayValues['SecondDimension'];
                }

                // Insert parameter
                $stmt = $this->db->prepare("
                    INSERT INTO parameters (project_id, gdl_name, gdl_type, default_value_json, is_fix_name, flag_bold, flag_child, flag_hidden, flag_unique, array_type, array_first_dim, array_second_dim, sort_order)
                    VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
                ");
                $stmt->execute([
                    $projectId, $gdlName, $gdlType, $defaultValue,
                    $isFixName, $flagBold, $flagChild, $flagHidden, $flagUnique,
                    $arrayType, $firstDim, $secondDim, $sortOrder
                ]);
                $paramId = $this->db->lastInsertId();

                // Insert translations
                $stmt = $this->db->prepare("
                    INSERT INTO parameter_translations (param_id, language_code, description)
                    VALUES (?, ?, ?)
                ");
                $stmt->execute([$paramId, 'de', $description]);
                $stmt->execute([$paramId, 'en', $description]);
            }

            $this->db->commit();

            return $this->jsonResponse($response, [
                'message' => 'Parameters imported successfully for project ' . $projectName . '.',
                'projectId' => $projectId
            ]);

        } catch (\PDOException $e) {
            $this->db->rollBack();
            error_log("DB Error during XML Import: " . $e->getMessage());
            return $this->jsonResponse($response, ['error' => 'Database error during import: ' . $e->getMessage()], 500);
        } catch (\Exception $e) {
            $this->db->rollBack();
            error_log("XML Import Error: " . $e->getMessage());
            return $this->jsonResponse($response, ['error' => 'Failed to import parameters: ' . $e->getMessage()], 500);
        }
    }

    public function getProjectParameters(Request $request, Response $response, array $args): Response
    {
        $projectId = $args['projectId'] ?? null;

        if (!$projectId) {
            return $this->jsonResponse($response, ['error' => 'Project ID is required.'], 400);
        }

        try {
            $stmt = $this->db->prepare("
                SELECT p.*, pt.language_code, pt.description, pt.values_list, pt.ui_tooltip
                FROM parameters p
                LEFT JOIN parameter_translations pt ON p.id = pt.param_id
                WHERE p.project_id = ?
                ORDER BY p.sort_order ASC
            ");
            $stmt->execute([$projectId]);
            $rawParams = $stmt->fetchAll(PDO::FETCH_ASSOC);

            $parameters = [];
            foreach ($rawParams as $row) {
                $paramId = $row['id'];
                if (!isset($parameters[$paramId])) {
                    $parameters[$paramId] = [
                        'id' => $row['id'],
                        'gdl_name' => $row['gdl_name'],
                        'gdl_type' => $row['gdl_type'],
                        'function_group' => $row['function_group'],
                        'array_type' => $row['array_type'],
                        'array_first_dim' => $row['array_first_dim'],
                        'array_second_dim' => $row['array_second_dim'],
                        'default_value_json' => $row['default_value_json'],
                        'is_fix_name' => (bool)$row['is_fix_name'],
                        'flag_bold' => (bool)$row['flag_bold'],
                        'flag_child' => (bool)$row['flag_child'],
                        'flag_hidden' => (bool)$row['flag_hidden'],
                        'flag_unique' => (bool)$row['flag_unique'],
                        'ui_page' => $row['ui_page'],
                        'is_ui_element' => (bool)$row['is_ui_element'],
                        'ui_code' => $row['ui_code'],
                        'sort_order' => $row['sort_order'],
                        'created_at' => $row['created_at'],
                        'updated_at' => $row['updated_at'],
                        'translations' => []
                    ];
                }
                if ($row['language_code']) {
                    $parameters[$paramId]['translations'][] = [
                        'language_code' => $row['language_code'],
                        'description' => $row['description'],
                        'values_list' => $row['values_list'],
                        'ui_tooltip' => $row['ui_tooltip']
                    ];
                }
            }

            $projectStmt = $this->db->prepare("SELECT name FROM projects WHERE id = ?");
            $projectStmt->execute([$projectId]);
            $projectName = $projectStmt->fetchColumn();

            return $this->jsonResponse($response, [
                'project_name' => $projectName,
                'parameters' => array_values($parameters)
            ]);

        } catch (\Exception $e) {
            error_log("Error fetching parameters: " . $e->getMessage());
            return $this->jsonResponse($response, ['error' => 'Failed to fetch parameters: ' . $e->getMessage()], 500);
        }
    }
}

// Helper function to convert SimpleXMLElement to array (for Dictionary)
function simplexml_to_array(\SimpleXMLElement $xml): array
{
    $array = [];
    foreach ($xml->children() as $node) {
        $name = $node->getName();
        if ($node->children()->count() > 0) {
            $array[$name] = simplexml_to_array($node);
        } else {
            $array[$name] = (string)$node;
        }
    }
    return $array;
}
